## Configuration Guide

### Critical Configurations

#### Consumer Group Management

| Config | Default | Purpose |
|--------|---------|---------|
| `group.id` | - | Consumer group identifier (required for group management) |
| `group.protocol` | `consumer` | Group coordination protocol: `consumer` (new) or `classic` (old) |
| `group.instance.id` | - | Static group member ID (enables rack-aware assignment) |

#### Offset Management

| Config | Default | Purpose |
|--------|---------|---------|
| `enable.auto.commit` | `true` | Automatically commit offsets periodically |
| `auto.commit.interval.ms` | 5000 | Auto-commit interval in milliseconds |
| `auto.offset.reset` | `latest` | Behavior when no committed offset: `earliest`, `latest`, `none` |

#### Polling and Timeouts

| Config | Default | Purpose |
|--------|---------|---------|
| `max.poll.interval.ms` | 300000 | Max time between polls before consumer leaves group |
| `max.poll.records` | 500 | Max records returned per poll (controls batch size) |
| `fetch.max.wait.ms` | 500 | Max wait for broker to accumulate fetch size |
| `fetch.min.bytes` | 1 | Min bytes broker should wait to accumulate |
| `default.api.timeout.ms` | 60000 | Default timeout for most operations |

#### Heartbeat and Session

| Config | Default | Purpose |
|--------|---------|---------|
| `heartbeat.interval.ms` | 3000 | Heartbeat interval (should be 1/3 of session.timeout.ms) |
| `session.timeout.ms` | 10000 | Time before consumer presumed dead |

#### Offset and Commits

| Config | Default | Purpose |
|--------|---------|---------|
| `isolation.level` | `read_uncommitted` | Transactional visibility: `read_uncommitted`, `read_committed` |
| `enable.auto.commit` | `true` | Enable periodic offset commits |

#### Network and Serialization

| Config | Default | Purpose |
|--------|---------|---------|
| `bootstrap.servers` | - | Broker addresses (comma-separated) |
| `key.deserializer` | - | Key deserializer class |
| `value.deserializer` | - | Value deserializer class |
| `connections.max.idle.ms` | 540000 | Max idle connection time before close |

### Tuning for Different Scenarios

#### High Throughput, Lower Latency

```properties
# Fetch more data at once
max.poll.records=1000
fetch.min.bytes=10000
fetch.max.wait.ms=100

# Faster heartbeat for quicker failure detection
heartbeat.interval.ms=1000
session.timeout.ms=5000
```

#### Large Message Batches, Longer Processing

```properties
# Allow more time between polls
max.poll.interval.ms=600000      # 10 minutes

# Batch size matches processing
max.poll.records=100

# Conservative commit interval
auto.commit.interval.ms=10000
```

#### Exactly-Once Semantics

```properties
# Disable auto-commit
enable.auto.commit=false

# Read only committed transactions
isolation.level=read_committed

# Use manual commitSync() after processing
```

#### Fault Tolerance / Rapid Failure Detection

```properties
# Quick detection of consumer failure
heartbeat.interval.ms=1000
session.timeout.ms=6000

# Quick rebalance on membership changes
partition.assignment.strategy=cooperative-sticky
```

